quran[154]{c,v,t}:
  12,53,WE MA ‘UBERRI’U NEFSI ‘INNE EN-NEFSE LE’EMMARETUN BIS-SU’I ‘ILLA MA REHIME RABBI ‘INNE RABBI GAFURUN REHIMUN
  12,54,WE KALEL-MELIKU E’TUNI BIHI ‘ESTEHLISHU LINEFSI FELEMMA KELLEMEHU KALE ‘INNEKEL-JEWME LEDEJNA MEKINUN ‘EMINUN
  12,55,KALE EXH’ALNI ‘ALA HAZA’INIL-’ERDI ‘INNI HEFIDHUN ‘ALIMUN
  12,56,WE KEDHELIKE MEKKENNA LIJUSUFE FIL-’ERDI JETEBEWWE’U MINHA HEJTHU JESHA’U NUSIBU BIREHMETINA MEN NESHA’U WE LA NUDI’U ‘EXHREL-MUHSININE
  12,57,WE LE’EXHRUL-’AHIRETI HAJRUN LILLEDHINE ‘AMENU WE KANU JETTEKUNE
  12,58,WE XHA’E ‘IHWETU JUSUFE FEDEHALU ‘ALEJHI FE’AREFEHUM WE HUM LEHU MUNKIRUNE
  12,59,WE LEMMA XHEHHEZEHUM BIXHEHAZIHIM KALE E’TUNI BI’EHIN LEKUM MIN ‘EBIKUM ‘ELA TEREWNE ‘ENNI ‘UFIL-KEJLE WE ‘ENA HAJRUL-MUNZILINE
  12,60,FE’IN LEM TE’TUNI BIHI FELA KEJLE LEKUM ‘INDI WE LA TEKREBUNI
  12,61,KALU SENURAWIDU ‘ANHU ‘EBAHU WE ‘INNA LEFA’ILUNE
  12,62,WE KALE LIFITJANIHI EXH’ALU BIDA’ATEHUM FI RIHALIHIM LE’ALLEHUM JA’RIFUNEHA ‘IDHA ENKALEBU ‘ILA ‘EHLIHIM LE’ALLEHUM JERXHI’UNE
  12,63,FELEMMA REXHA’U ‘ILA ‘EBIHIM KALU JA ‘EBANA MUNI’A MINNAL-KEJLU FE’ERSIL ME’ANA ‘EHANA NEKTEL WE ‘INNA LEHU LEHAFIDHUNE
  12,64,KALE HEL ‘AMENUKUM ‘ALEJHI ‘ILLA KEMA ‘EMINTUKUM ‘ALA ‘EHIHI MIN KABLU FE-ELLAHU HAJRUN HAFIDHÆN WE HUWE ‘ERHEMU ER-RAHIMINE
  12,65,WE LEMMA FETEHU META’AHUM WE XHEDU BIDA’ATEHUM RUDDET ‘ILEJHIM KALU JA ‘EBANA MA NEBGI HEDHIHI BIDA’ATUNA RUDDET ‘ILEJNA WE NEMIRU ‘EHLENA WE NEHFEDHU ‘EHANA WE NEZDADU KEJLE BA’IRIN DHALIKE KEJLUN JESIRUN
  12,66,KALE LEN ‘URSILEHU ME’AKUM HETTA TU’UTUNI MEWTHIKÆN MINEL-LAHI LETE’TUNENI BIHI ‘ILLA ‘EN JUHATE BIKUM FELEMMA ‘ATEWHU MEWTHIKAHUM KALEL-LAHU ‘ALA MA NEKULU WE KILUN
  12,67,WE KALE JA BENIJE LA TEDHULU MIN BABIN WAHIDIN WE EDHULU MIN ‘EBWABIN MUTEFERRIKATIN WE MA ‘UGNI ‘ANKUM MINEL-LAHI MIN SHEJ’IN ‘INIL-HUKMU ‘ILLA LILLAHI ‘ALEJHI TEWEKKELTU WE ‘ALEJHI FELJETEWEKKELIL-MUTEWEKKILUNE
  12,68,WE LEMMA DEHALU MIN HEJTHU ‘EMEREHUM ‘EBUHUM MMA KANE JUGNI ‘ANHUM MMINEL-LAHI MIN SHEJ’IN ‘ILLA HAXHETEN FI NEFSI JA’KUBE KADAHA WE ‘INNEHU LEDHU ‘ILMIN LIMA ‘ALLEMNAHU WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JA’LEMUNE
  12,69,WE LEMMA DEHALU ‘ALA JUSUFE ‘AWA ‘ILEJHI ‘EHAHU KALE ‘INNI ‘ENA ‘EHUKE FELA TEBTE’IS BIMA KANU JA’MELUNE
  12,70,FELEMMA XHEHHEZEHUM BIXHEHAZIHIM XHE’ALE ES-SIKAJETE FI REHLI ‘EHIHI THUMME ‘EDHDHENE MU’UEDHDHINUN ‘EJJETUHAL-’IRU ‘INNEKUM LESARIKUNE
  12,71,KALU WE ‘EKBELU ‘ALEJHIM MADHA TEFKIDUNE
  12,72,KALU NEFKIDU SUWA’AL-MELIKI WE LIMEN XHA’E BIHI HIMLU BA’IRIN WE ‘ENA BIHI ZA’IMUN
  12,73,KALU TE-ELLAHI LEKAD ‘ALIMTUM MA XHI’NA LINUFSIDE FIL-’ERDI WE MA KUNNA SARIKINE
  12,74,KALU FEMA XHEZA’UUHU ‘IN KUNTUM KADHIBINE
  12,75,KALU XHEZA’UUHU MEN WUXHIDE FI REHLIHI FEHUWE XHEZA’UUHU KEDHALIKE NEXHZI EDH-DHALIMINE
  12,76,FEBEDE’E BI’EW’IJETIHIM KABLE WI’A’I ‘EHIHI THUMME ESTEHREXHEHA MIN WI’A’I ‘EHIHI KEDHALIKE KIDNA LIJUSUFE MA KANE LIJE’HUDHE ‘EHAHU FI DINIL-MELIKI ‘ILLA ‘EN JESHA’EL-LAHU NERFA’U DEREXHATIN MEN NESHA’U WE FEWKA KULLI DHI ‘ILMIN ‘ALIMUN
  12,77,KALU ‘IN JESRIK FEKAD SEREKA ‘EHUN LEHU MIN KABLU FE’ESERREHA JUSUFU FI NEFSIHI WE LEM JUBDIHA LEHUM KALE ‘ENTUM SHERRUN MEKANÆN WEL-LAHU ‘A’LEMU BIMA TESIFUNE
  12,78,KALU JA ‘EJJUHAL-’AZIZU ‘INNE LEHU ‘EBÆN SHEJHÆN KEBIRÆN FEHUDH ‘EHEDENA MEKANEHU ‘INNA NERAKE MINEL-MUHSININE
  12,79,KALE MA’ADHEL-LAHI ‘EN NE’HUDHE ‘ILLA MEN WEXHEDNA META’ANA ‘INDEHU ‘INNA ‘IDHÆN LEDHALIMUNE
  12,80,FELEMMA ESTEJ’ESU MINHU HALESU NEXHIJÆN KALE KEBIRUHUM ‘ELEM TA’LEMU ‘ENNE ‘EBAKUM KAD ‘EHADHE ‘ALEJKUM MEWTHIKÆN MINEL-LAHI WE MIN KABLU MA FERRETTUM FI JUSUFE FELEN ‘EBREHEL-’ERDE HETTA JE’DHENE LI ‘EBI ‘EW JEHKUMEL-LAHU LI WE HUWE HAJRUL-HAKIMINE
  12,81,ERXHI’U ‘ILA ‘EBIKUM FEKULU JA ‘EBANA ‘INNE EBNEKE SEREKA WE MA SHEHIDNA ‘ILLA BIMA ‘ALIMNA WE MA KUNNA LILGAJBI HAFIDHINE
  12,82,WE ES’ELIL-KARJETEL-LETI KUNNA FIHA WEL-’IREL-LETI ‘EKBELNA FIHA WE ‘INNA LESADIKUNE
  12,83,KALE BEL SEWWELET LEKUM ‘ENFUSUKUM ‘EMRÆN FESEBRUN XHEMILUN ‘ASALLAHU ‘EN JE’TIJENI BIHIM XHEMI’ÆN ‘INNEHU HUWEL-’ALIMUL-HEKIMU
  12,84,WE TEWELLA ‘ANHUM WE KALE JA ‘ESEFA ‘ALA JUSUFE WE EBJEDDET ‘AJNAHU MINEL-HUZNI FEHUWE KEDHIMUN
  12,85,KALU TE-ELLAHI TEFTE’U TEDHKURU JUSUFE HETTA TEKUNE HEREDÆN ‘EW TEKUNE MINEL-HALIKINE
  12,86,KALE ‘INNEMA ‘ESHKU BETHTHI WE HUZNI ‘ILA ELLAHI WE ‘A’LEMU MINEL-LAHI MA LA TA’LEMUNE
  12,87,JA BENIJE EDH/HEBU FETEHESSESU MIN JUSUFE WE ‘EHIHI WE LA TEJ’ESU MIN REWHI ELLAHI ‘INNEHU LA JEJ’ESU MIN REWHI ELLAHI ‘ILLAL-KAWMUL-KAFIRUNE
  12,88,FELEMMA DEHALU ‘ALEJHI KALU JA ‘EJJUHAL-’AZIZU MESSENA WE ‘EHLENA ED-DURRU WE XHI’NA BIBIDA’ATIN MUZXHÆTIN FE’EWFI LENAL-KEJLE WE TESEDDEK ‘ALEJNA ‘INNALL-LLAHE JEXHZIL-MUTESEDDIKINE
  12,89,KALE HEL ‘ALIMTUM MA FE’ALTUM BIJUSUFE WE ‘EHIHI ‘IDH ‘ENTUM XHAHILUNE
  12,90,KALU ‘E’INNEKE LE’ENTE JUSUFU KALE ‘ENA JUSUFU WE HEDHA ‘EHI KAD MENNEL-LAHU ‘ALEJNA ‘INNEHU MEN JETTEKI WE JESBIR FE’INNALL-LLAHE LA JUDI’U ‘EXHREL-MUHSININE
  12,91,KALU TE-ELLAHI LEKAD ‘ATHEREKEL-LAHU ‘ALEJNA WE ‘IN KUNNA LEHATI’INE
  12,92,KALE LA TETHRIBE ‘ALEJKUMUL-JEWME JEGFIRU ELLAHU LEKUM WE HUWE ‘ERHEMU ER-RAHIMINE
  12,93,EDH/HEBU BIKAMISI HADHA FE’ELKUHU ‘ALA WEXHHI ‘EBI JE’TI BESIRÆN WE ‘TUNI BI’EHLIKUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  12,94,WE LEMMA FESELETIL-’IRU KALE ‘EBUHUM ‘INNI LE’EXHIDU RIHE JUSUFE LEWLA ‘EN TUFENNIDUNI
  12,95,KALU TE-ELLAHI ‘INNEKE LEFI DELALIKEL-KADIMI
  12,96,FELEMMA ‘EN XHA’EL-BESHIRU ‘ELKAHU ‘ALA WEXHHIHI FARTEDDE BESIRÆN KALE ‘ELEM ‘EKUL LEKUM ‘INNI ‘A’LEMU MINEL-LAHI MA LA TA’LEMUNE
  12,97,KALU JA ‘EBANA ESTEGFIR LENA DHUNUBENA ‘INNA KUNNA HATI’INE
  12,98,KALE SEWFE ‘ESTEGFIRU LEKUM RABBI ‘INNEHU HUWEL-GAFURU ER-REHIMU
  12,99,FELEMMA DEHALU ‘ALA JUSUFE ‘AWA ‘ILEJHI ‘EBEWEJHI WE KALE EDHULU MISRE ‘IN SHA’EL-LAHU ‘AMININE
  12,100,WE REFE’A ‘EBEWEJHI ‘ALEL-’ARSHI WE HARRU LEHU SUXHXHEDÆN WE KALE JA ‘EBETI HADHA TE’WILU RU’UJA J MIN KABLU KAD XHE’ALEHA RABBI HEKKÆN WE KAD ‘EHSENE BI ‘IDH ‘EHREXHENI MINE ES-SIXHNI WE XHA’E BIKUM MINEL-BEDWI MIN BA’DI ‘EN NEZEGA ESH-SHEJTANU BEJNI WE
  12,101,REBBI KAD ‘ATEJTENI MINEL-MULKI WE ‘ALLEMTENI MIN TE’WILIL-’EHADITHI FATIRE ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI ‘ENTE WE LIJI FI ED-DUNJA WEL-’AHIRETI TEWEFFENI MUSLIMÆN WE ‘ELHIKNI BIS-SALIHINE
  12,102,DHALIKE MIN ‘ENBA’IL-GAJBI NUHIHI ‘ILEJKE WE MA KUNTE LEDEJHIM ‘IDH ‘EXHMA’U ‘EMREHUM WE HUM JEMKURUNE
  12,103,WE MA ‘EKTHERU EN-NASI WE LEW HERESTE BIMU’UMININE
  12,104,WE MA TES’ELUHUM ‘ALEJHI MIN ‘EXHRIN ‘IN HUWE ‘ILLA DHIKRUN LIL’ALEMINE
  12,105,WE KE’EJJIN MIN ‘AJETIN FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI JEMURRUNE ‘ALEJHA WE HUM ‘ANHA MU’RIDUNE
  12,106,WE MA JU’UMINU ‘EKTHERUHUM BILLAHI ‘ILLA WE HUM MUSHRIKUNE
  12,107,‘EFE’EMINU ‘EN TE’TIJEHUM GASHIJETUN MIN ‘ADHABI ELLAHI ‘EW TE’TIJEHUMU ES-SA’ATU BEGTETEN WE HUM LA JESH’URUNE
  12,108,KUL HEDHIHI SEBILI ‘ED’U ‘ILA ELLAHI ‘ALA BESIRETIN ‘ENA WE MENI ETTEBE’ANI WE SUBHANEL-LAHI WE MA ‘ENA MINEL-MUSHRIKINE
  12,109,WE MA ‘ERSELNA MIN KABLIKE ‘ILLA RIXHALÆN NUHI ‘ILEJHIM MIN ‘EHLIL-KURA ‘EFELEM JESIRU FIL-’ERDI FEJENDHURU KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM WE LEDARUL-’AHIRETI HAJRUN LILLEDHINE ETTEKAW ‘EFELA TA’KILUNE
  12,110,HETTA ‘IDHA ESTEJ’ESE ER-RUSULU WE DHENNU ‘ENNEHUM KAD KUDHIBU XHA’EHUM NESRUNA FENUXHXHIJE MEN NESHA’U WE LA JUREDDU BE’SUNA ‘ANIL-KAWMIL-MUXHRIMINE
  12,111,LEKAD KANE FI KASESIHIM ‘IBRETUN LI’WLIL-’ELBABI MA KANE HEDITHÆN JUFTERA WE LEKIN TESDIKAL-LEDHI BEJNE JEDEJHI WE TEFSILE KULLI SHEJ’IN WE HUDEN WE REHMETEN LIKAWMIN JU’UMINUNE
  13,1,‘ELIF-LAM-MIM-RA TILKE ‘AJATUL-KITABI WEL-LEDHI ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJKE MIN RABBIKEL-HEKKU WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JU’UMINUNE
  13,2,ELLAHUL-LEDHI REFE’A ES-SEMAWATI BIGAJRI ‘AMEDIN TEREWNEHA THUMME ESTEWA ‘ALEL-’ARSHI WE SEHHARE ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE KULLUN JEXHRI LI’XHELIN MUSEMMEN JUDEBBIRUL-’EMRE JUFESSILUL-’AJATI LE’ALLEKUM BILIKA’I RABBIKUM TUKINUNE
  13,3,WE HUWEL-LEDHI MEDDEL-’ERDE WE XHE’ALE FIHA REWASIJE WE ‘ENHARÆN WE MIN KULLI ETH-THEMERATI XHE’ALE FIHA ZEWXHEJNI ETHNEJNI JUGSHIL-LEJLE EN-NEHARE ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JETEFEKKERUNE
  13,4,WE FIL-’ERDI KITA’UN MUTEXHAWIRATUN WE XHENNATUN MIN ‘A’NABIN WE ZER’UN WE NEHILUN SINWANUN WE GAJRU SINWANIN JUSKA BIMA’IN WAHIDIN WE NUFEDDILU BA’DEHA ‘ALA BA’DIN FIL-’UKULI ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JA’KILUNE
  13,5,WE ‘IN TA’XHEB FE’AXHEBUN KAWLUHUM ‘E’IDHA KUNNA TURABÆN ‘E’INNA LEFI HALKIN XHEDIDIN ‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE KEFERU BIREBBIHIM WE ‘ULA’IKEL-’EGLALU FI ‘A’NAKIHIM WE ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABU EN-NARI HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  13,6,WE JESTA’XHILUNEKE BIS-SEJJI’ETI KABLEL-HESENETI WE KAD HALET MIN KABLIHIMUL-METHULATU WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LEDHU MEGFIRETIN LILNNASI ‘ALA DHULMIHIM WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LESHEDIDUL-’IKABI
  13,7,WE JEKULUL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ALEJHI ‘AJETUN MIN RABBIHI ‘INNEMA ‘ENTE MUNDHIRUN WE LIKULLI KAWMIN HADIN
  13,8,ELLAHU JA’LEMU MA TEHMILU KULLU ‘UNTHA WE MA TEGIDUL-’ERHAMU WE MA TEZDADU WE KULLU SHEJ’IN ‘INDEHU BIMIKDARIN
  13,9,‘ALIMUL-GAJBI WE ESH-SHEHADETIL-KEBIRUL-MUTA’ALI
  13,10,SEWA’UN MINKUM MEN ‘ESERREL-KAWLE WE MEN XHEHERE BIHI WE MEN HUWE MUSTEHFIN BIL-LEJLI WE SARIBUN BIN-NEHARI
  13,11,LEHU MU’AKKIBATUN MIN BEJNI JEDEJHI WE MIN HALFIHI JEHFEDHUNEHU MIN ‘EMRI ELLAHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JUGAJJIRU MA BIKAWMIN HETTA JUGAJJIRU MA BI’ENFUSIHIM WE ‘IDHA ‘ERADEL-LAHU BIKAWMIN SU’ÆN FELA MEREDDE LEHU WE MA LEHUM MIN DUNIHI MIN WE E
  13,12,HUWEL-LEDHI JURIKUMUL-BERKA HAWFÆN WE TEMA’ÆN WE JUNSHI’U ES-SEHABE ETH-THIKALE
  13,13,WE JUSEBBIHU ER-RA’DU BIHEMDIHI WEL-MELA’IKETU MIN HIFETIHI WE JURSILU ES-SEWA’IKA FEJUSIBU BIHA MEN JESHA’U WE HUM JUXHADILUNE FI ELLAHI WE HUWE SHEDIDUL-MIHALI
  13,14,LEHU DA’WETUL-HEKKI WEL-LEDHINE JED’UNE MIN DUNIHI LA JESTEXHIBUNE LEHUM BISHEJ’IN ‘ILLA KEBASITI KEFFEJHI ‘ILAL-MA’I LIJEBLUGA FAHU WE MA HUWE BIBALIGIHI WE MA DU’A’UL-KAFIRINE ‘ILLA FI DELALIN
  13,15,WE LILLEHI JESXHUDU MEN FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI TEW’ÆN WE KERHÆN WE DHILALUHUM BIL-GUDUWI WEL-’ASALI
  13,16,KUL MEN REBBU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI KULI ELLAHU KUL ‘EFATTEHADHTUM MIN DUNIHI ‘EWLIJA’E LA JEMLIKUNE LI’NFUSIHIM NEF’ÆN WE LA DERRÆN KUL HEL JESTEWIL-’A’MA WEL-BESIRU ‘EM HEL TESTEWI EDH-DHULUMATU WE EN-NUR ‘EM XHE’ALU LILLAHI SHUREKA’E HALEKU KEHALKIHI F
  13,17,‘ENZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FESALET ‘EWDIJETUN BIKADERIHA FAHTEMELE ES-SEJLU ZEBEDÆN RABIÆN WE MIMMA JUKIDUNE ‘ALEJHI FI EN-NARI EBTIGA’E HILJETIN ‘EW META’IN ZEBEDUN MITHLUHU KEDHALIKE JEDRIBU ELLAHUL-HEKKA WEL-BATILE FE’EMMA EZ-ZEBEDU FEJEDH/HEBU XHUFA
  13,18,LILLEDHINE ESTEXHABU LIREBBIHIMUL-HUSNA WEL-LEDHINE LEM JESTEXHIBU LEHU LEW ‘ENNE LEHUM MA FIL-’ERDI XHEMI’ÆN WE MITHLEHU ME’AHU LAFTEDEW BIHI ‘ULA’IKE LEHUM SU’UL-HISABI WE ME’WAHUM XHEHENNEMU WE BI’SEL-MIHADU
  13,19,‘EFEMEN JA’LEMU ‘ENNEMA ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJKE MIN RABBIKEL-HEKKU KEMEN HUWE ‘A’MA ‘INNEMA JETEDHEKKERU ‘ULUL-’ELBABI
  13,20,EL-LEDHINE JUFUNE BI’AHDI ELLAHI WE LA JENKUDUNEL-MITHAKA
  13,21,WEL-LEDHINE JESILUNE MA ‘EMEREL-LAHU BIHI ‘EN JUSELE WE JEHSHEWNE REBBEHUM WE JEHAFUNE SU’EL-HISABI
  13,22,WEL-LEDHINE SEBERU EBTIGA’E WEXHHI RABBIHIM WE ‘EKAMU ES-SELÆTE WE ‘ENFEKU MIMMA REZEKNAHUM SIRRÆN WE ‘ALANIJETEN WE JEDRE’UNE BIL-HESENETI ES-SEJJI’ETE ‘ULA’IKE LEHUM ‘UKBA ED-DARI
  13,23,XHENNATU ‘ADNIN JEDHULUNEHA WE MEN SELEHE MIN ‘ABA’IHIM WE ‘EZWAXHIHIM WE DHURRIJATIHIM WEL-MELA’IKETU JEDHULUNE ‘ALEJHIM MIN KULLI BABIN
  13,24,SELAMUN ‘ALEJKUM BIMA SEBERTUM FENI’ME ‘UKBA ED-DARI
  13,25,WEL-LEDHINE JENKUDUNE ‘AHDEL-LAHI MIN BA’DI MITHAKIHI WE JEKTA’UNE MA ‘EMEREL-LAHU BIHI ‘EN JUSELE WE JUFSIDUNE FIL-’ERDI ‘ULA’IKE LEHUMUL-LA’NETU WE LEHUM SU’U ED-DARI
  13,26,ELLAHU JEBSUTU ER-RIZKA LIMEN JESHA’U WE JEKDIRU WE FERIHU BIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE MAL-HEJÆTU ED-DUNJA FIL-’AHIRETI ‘ILLA META’UN
  13,27,WE JEKULUL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ALEJHI ‘AJETUN MIN RABBIHI KUL ‘INNALL-LLAHE JUDILLU MEN JESHA’U WE JEHDI ‘ILEJHI MEN ‘ENABE
  13,28,EL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE TETME’INNU KULUBUHUM BIDHIKRI ELLAHI ‘ELA BIDHIKRI ELLAHI TETME’INNUL-KULUBU
  13,29,EL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI TUBA LEHUM WE HUSNU ME’ABIN
  13,30,KEDHALIKE ‘ERSELNAKE FI ‘UMMETIN KAD HALET MIN KABLIHA ‘UMEMUN LITETLUWE ‘ALEJHIMUL-LEDHI ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILEJKE WE HUM JEKFURUNE BIR-REHMENI KUL HUWE RABBI LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE ‘ALEJHI TEWEKKELTU WE ‘ILEJHI METABI
  13,31,WE LEW ‘ENNE KUR’ANÆN SUJJIRET BIHIL-XHIBALU ‘EW KUTTI’AT BIHIL-’ERDU ‘EW KULLIME BIHIL-MEWTA BEL LILLAHIL-’EMRU XHEMI’ÆN ‘EFELEM JEJ’ESIL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘EN LEW JESHA’U ELLAHU LEHEDA EN-NASE XHEMI’ÆN WE LA JEZALUL-LEDHINE KEFERU TUSIBUHUM BIMA SENA’U KAR
  13,32,WE LEKADI ESTUHZI’E BIRUSULIN MIN KABLIKE FE’EMLEJTU LILLEDHINE KEFERU THUMME ‘EHADHTUHUM FEKEJFE KANE ‘IKABI
  13,33,‘EFEMEN HUWE KA’IMUN ‘ALA KULLI NEFSIN BIMA KESEBET WE XHE’ALU LILLAHI SHUREKA’E KUL SEMMUHUM ‘EM TUNEBBI’UNEHU BIMA LA JA’LEMU FIL-’ERDI ‘EM BIDHAHIRIN MINEL-KAWLI BEL ZUJJINE LILLEDHINE KEFERU MEKRUHUM WE SUDDU ‘ANI ES-SEBILI WE MEN JUDLILI ELLAHU FEMA
  13,34,LEHUM ‘ADHABUN FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE LE’ADHABUL-’AHIRETI ‘ESHEKKU WE MA LEHUM MINEL-LAHI MIN WAKIN
  13,35,METHELUL-XHENNETI ELLETI WU’IDEL-MUTTEKUNE TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU ‘UKULUHA DA’IMUN WE DHILLUHA TILKE ‘UKBAL-LEDHINE ETTEKAW WE ‘UKBAL-KAFIRINE EN-NARU
  13,36,WEL-LEDHINE ‘ATEJNAHUMUL-KITABE JEFREHUNE BIMA ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJKE WE MINEL-’EHZABI MEN JUNKIRU BA’DEHU KUL ‘INNEMA ‘UMIRTU ‘EN ‘A’BUDEL-LAHE WE LA ‘USHRIKE BIHI ‘ILEJHI ‘ED’U WE ‘ILEJHI ME’ABI
  13,37,WE KEDHELIKE ‘ENZELNAHU HUKMÆN ‘AREBIJÆN WE LE’INI ETTEBA’TE ‘EHWA’EHUM BA’DEMA XHA’EKE MINEL-’ILMI MA LEKE MINEL-LAHI MIN WE LIJIN WE LA WAKIN
  13,38,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA RUSULÆN MIN KABLIKE WE XHE’ALNA LEHUM ‘EZWAXHÆN WE DHURRIJETEN WE MA KANE LIRESULIN ‘EN JE’TIJE BI’AJETIN ‘ILLA BI’IDHNI ELLAHI LIKULLI ‘EXHELIN KITABUN
  13,39,JEMHU ELLAHU MA JESHA’U WE JUTHBITU WE ‘INDEHU ‘UMMUL-KITABI
  13,40,WE ‘IN MA NURIJENNEKE BA’DEL-LEDHI NA’IDUHUM ‘EW NETEWEFFEJENNEKE FE’INNEMA ‘ALEJKEL-BELAGU WE ‘ALEJNAL-HISABU
  13,41,‘EWELEM JEREW ‘ENNA NE’TIL-’ERDE NENKUSUHA MIN ‘ETRAFIHA WEL-LAHU JEHKUMU LA MU’AKKIBE LIHUKMIHI WE HUWE SERI’UL-HISABI
  13,42,WE KAD MEKEREL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM FELILLAHIL-MEKRU XHEMI’ÆN JA’LEMU MA TEKSIBU KULLU NEFSIN WE SEJA’LEMUL-KUFFARU LIMEN ‘UKBA ED-DARI
  13,43,WE JEKULUL-LEDHINE KEFERU LESTE MURSELÆN KUL KEFA BILLAHI SHEHIDÆN BEJNI WE BEJNEKUM WE MEN ‘INDEHU ‘ILMUL-KITABI
  14,1,‘ELIF-LAM-RA KITABUN ‘ENZELNAHU ‘ILEJKE LITUHRIXHE EN-NASE MINE EDH-DHULUMATI ‘ILA EN-NUR BI’IDHNI RABBIHIM ‘ILA SIRATIL-’AZIZIL-HEMIDI
  14,2,ELLAHIL-LEDHI LEHU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI WE WEJLUN LILKAFIRINE MIN ‘ADHABIN SHEDIDIN
  14,3,EL-LEDHINE JESTEHIBBUNEL-HEJÆTE ED-DUNJA ‘ALEL-’AHIRETI WE JESUDDUNE ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI WE JEBGUNEHA ‘IWEXHÆN ‘ULA’IKE FI DELALIN BA’IDIN
  14,4,WE MA ‘ERSELNA MIN RESULIN ‘ILLA BILISANI KAWMIHI LIJUBEJJINE LEHUM FEJUDILLU ELLAHU MEN JESHA’U WE JEHDI MEN JESHA’U WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  14,5,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA MUSA BI’AJATINA ‘EN ‘EHRIXH KAWMEKE MINE EDH-DHULUMATI ‘ILA EN-NURI WE DHEKKIRHUM BI’EJJAMI ELLAHI ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKULLI SEBBARIN SHEKURIN
  14,6,WE ‘IDH KALE MUSA LIKAWMIHI EDHKURU NI’METEL-LAHI ‘ALEJKUM ‘IDH ‘ENXHAKUM MIN ‘ALI FIR’AWNE JESUMUNEKUM SU’EL-’ADHABI WE JUDHEBBIHUNE ‘EBNA’EKUM WE JESTEHJUNE NISA’EKUM WE FI DHALIKUM BELA’UN MIN RABBIKUM ‘ADHIMUN
  14,7,WE ‘IDH TE’EDHDHENE REBBUKUM LE’IN SHEKERTUM LE’EZIDENNEKUM WE LE’IN KEFERTUM ‘INNE ‘ADHABI LESHEDIDUN
  14,8,WE KALE MUSA ‘IN TEKFURU ‘ENTUM WE MEN FIL-’ERDI XHEMI’ÆN FE’INNALL-LLAHE LEGANIJUN HEMIDUN
  14,9,‘ELEM JE’TIKUM NEBE’UL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIKUM KAWMI NUHIN WE ‘ADIN WE THEMUDE WEL-LEDHINE MIN BA’DIHIM LA JA’LEMUHUM ‘ILLALLAHU XHA’ET/HUM RUSULUHUM BIL-BEJJINATI FEREDDU ‘EJDIJEHUM FI ‘EFWAHIHIM WE KALU ‘INNA KEFERNA BIMA ‘URSILTUM BIHI WE ‘INNA LEFI SHEKK
  14,10,KALET RUSULUHUM ‘EFI ELLAHI SHEKKUN FATIRI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI JED’UKUM LIJEGFIRE LEKUM MIN DHUNUBIKUM WE JU’UEHHIREKUM ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN KALU ‘IN ‘ENTUM ‘ILLA BESHERUN MITHLUNA TURIDUNE ‘EN TESUDDUNA ‘AMMA KANE JA’BUDU ‘ABA’UUNA FE’TUNA BISULTANIN
  14,11,KALET LEHUM RUSULUHUM ‘IN NEHNU ‘ILLA BESHERUN MITHLUKUM WE LEKINNALL-LLAHE JEMUNNU ‘ALA MEN JESHA’U MIN ‘IBADIHI WE MA KANE LENA ‘EN NE’TIJEKUM BISULTANIN ‘ILLA BI’IDHNI ELLAHI WE ‘ALA ELLAHI FELJETEWEKKELIL-MU’UMINUNE
  14,12,WE MA LENA ‘ELLA NETEWEKKELE ‘ALA ELLAHI WE KAD HEDANA SUBULENA WE LENESBIRENNE ‘ALA MA ‘ADHEJTUMUNA WE ‘ALA ELLAHI FELJETEWEKKELIL-MUTEWEKKILUNE
  14,13,WE KALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LIRUSULIHIM LENUHRIXHENNEKUM MIN ‘ERDINA ‘EW LETA’UDUNNE FI MILLETINA FE’EWHA ‘ILEJHIM REBBUHUM LENUHLIKENNE EDH-DHALIMINE
  14,14,WE LENUSKINENNEKUMUL-’ERDE MIN BA’DIHIM DHALIKE LIMEN HAFE MEKAMI WE HAFE WA’IDI
  14,15,WE ESTEFTEHU WE HABE KULLU XHEBBARIN ‘ANIDIN
  14,16,MIN WERA’IHI XHEHENNEMU WE JUSKA MIN MA’IN SEDIDIN
  14,17,JETEXHERRA’UHU WE LA JEKADU JUSIGUHU WE JE’TIHIL-MEWTU MIN KULLI MEKANIN WE MA HUWE BIMEJJITIN WE MIN WERA’IHI ‘ADHABUN GALIDHUN
  14,18,METHELUL-LEDHINE KEFERU BIREBBIHIM ‘A’MALUHUM KEREMADIN ESHTEDDET BIHI ER-RIHU FI JEWMIN ‘ASIFIN LA JEKDIRUNE MIMMA KESEBU ‘ALA SHEJ’IN DHALIKE HUWE ED-DELALUL-BA’IDU
  14,19,‘ELEM TERA ‘ENNEL-LAHE HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE BIL-HEKKI ‘IN JESHE’ JUDH/HIBKUM WE JE’TI BIHALKIN XHEDIDIN
  14,20,WE MA DHALIKE ‘ALA ELLAHI BI’AZIZIN
  14,21,WE BEREZU LILLAHI XHEMI’ÆN FEKALE ED-DU’AFA’U LILLEDHINE ESTEKBERU ‘INNA KUNNA LEKUM TEBA’ÆN FEHEL ‘ENTUM MUGNUNE ‘ANNA MIN ‘ADHABI ELLAHI MIN SHEJ’IN KALU LEW HEDANALLAHU LEHEDEJNAKUM SEWA’UN ‘ALEJNA ‘EXHEZI’NA ‘EM SEBERNA MA LENA MIN MEHISIN
  14,22,WE KALE ESH-SHEJTANU LEMMA KUDIJEL-’EMRU ‘INNALL-LLAHE WE’ADEKUM WA’DEL-HEKKI WE WE’ADTUKUM FE’EHLEFTUKUM WE MA KANE LI ‘ALEJKUM MIN SULTANIN ‘ILLA ‘EN DE’AWTUKUM FASTEXHEBTUM LI FELA TELUMUNI WE LUMU ‘ENFUSEKUM MA ‘ENA BIMUSRIHIKUM WE MA ‘ENTUM BIMUSRIHI
  14,23,WE ‘UDHILEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI XHENNATIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU HALIDINE FIHA BI’IDHNI RABBIHIM TEHIJETUHUM FIHA SELAMUN
  14,24,‘ELEM TERA KEJFE DEREBEL-LAHU METHELÆN KELIMETEN TEJJIBETEN KESHEXHERETIN TEJJIBETIN ‘ESLUHA THABITUN WE FER’UHA FI ES-SEMA’I
  14,25,TU’UTI ‘UKULEHA KULLE HININ BI’IDHNI RABBIHA WE JEDRIBU ELLAHUL-’EMTHALE LILNNASI LE’ALLEHUM JETEDHEKKERUNE
  14,26,WE METHELU KELIMETIN HABITHETIN KESHEXHERETIN HABITHETIN EXHTUTHTHET MIN FEWKIL-’ERDI MA LEHA MIN KARARIN
  14,27,JUTHEBBITU ELLAHUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU BIL-KAWLI ETH-THABITI FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE FIL-’AHIRETI WE JUDILLU ELLAHU EDH-DHALIMINE WE JEF’ALU ELLAHU MA JESHA’U
  14,28,‘ELEM TERA ‘ILAL-LEDHINE BEDDELU NI’METEL-LAHI KUFRÆN WE ‘EHELLU KAWMEHUM DAREL-BEWARI
  14,29,XHEHENNEME JESLEWNEHA WE BI’SEL-KARARU
  14,30,WE XHE’ALU LILLAHI ‘ENDADÆN LIJUDILLU ‘AN SEBILIHI KUL TEMETTA’U FE’INNE MESIREKUM ‘ILA EN-NARI
  14,31,KUL LI’IBADIJEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU JUKIMU ES-SELÆTE WE JUNFIKU MIMMA REZEKNAHUM SIRRÆN WE ‘ALANIJETEN MIN KABLI ‘EN JE’TIJE JEWMUN LA BEJ’UN FIHI WE LA HILALUN
  14,32,ELLAHUL-LEDHI HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE WE ‘ENZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FE’EHREXHE BIHI MINE ETH-THEMERATI RIZKÆN LEKUM WE SEHHARE LEKUMUL-FULKE LITEXHRIJE FIL-BEHRI BI’EMRIHI WE SEHHARE LEKUMUL-’ENHARE
  14,33,WE SEHHARE LEKUMU ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE DA’IBEJNI WE SEHHARE LEKUMUL-LEJLE WE EN-NEHAR
  14,34,WE ‘ATAKUM MIN KULLI MA SE’ELTUMUHU WE ‘IN TA’UDDU NI’METEL-LAHI LA TUHSUHA ‘INNEL-’INSANE LEDHELUMUN KEFFARUN
  14,35,WE ‘IDH KALE ‘IBRAHIMU RABBI EXH’AL HADHAL-BELEDE ‘AMINÆN WE EXHNUBNI WE BENIJE ‘EN NA’BUDEL-’ESNAME
  14,36,REBBI ‘INNEHUNNE ‘EDLELNE KETHIRÆN MINE EN-NASI FEMEN TEBI’ANI FE’INNEHU MINNI WE MEN ‘ASANI FE’INNEKE GAFURUN REHIMUN
  14,37,REBBENA ‘INNI ‘ESKENTU MIN DHURRIJETI BIWADIN GAJRI DHI ZER’IN ‘INDE BEJTIKEL-MUHERREMI REBBENA LIJUKIMU ES-SELÆTE FAXH’AL ‘EF’IDETEN MINE EN-NASI TEHWI ‘ILEJHIM WE ERZUKHUM MINE ETH-THEMERATI LE’ALLEHUM JESHKURUNE
  14,38,REBBENA ‘INNEKE TA’LEMU MA NUHFI WE MA NU’LINU WE MA JEHFA ‘ALA ELLAHI MIN SHEJ’IN FIL-’ERDI WE LA FI ES-SEMA’I
  14,39,EL-HEMDU LILLAHIL-LEDHI WEHEBE LI ‘ALEL-KIBERI ‘ISMA’ILE WE ‘ISHAKA ‘INNE RABBI LESEMI’U ED-DU’A’I
  14,40,REBBI EXH’ALNI MUKIME ES-SELÆTI WE MIN DHURRIJETI REBBENA WE TEKABBEL DU’A’I
  14,41,REBBENA EGFIR LI WE LIWALIDEJJE WE LILMU’UMININE JEWME JEKUMUL-HISABU
  14,42,WE LA TEHSEBENNEL-LAHE GAFILÆN ‘AMMA JA’MELU EDH-DHALIMUNE ‘INNEMA JU’UEHHIRUHUM LIJEWMIN TESHHASU FIHIL-’EBSARU
  14,43,MUHTI’INE MUKNI’I RU’USIHIM LA JERTEDDU ‘ILEJHIM TERFUHUM WE ‘EF’IDETUHUM HEWA’UN
  14,44,WE ‘ENDHIRI EN-NASE JEWME JE’TIHIMUL-’ADHABU FEJEKULUL-LEDHINE DHELEMU REBBENA ‘EHHIRNA ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN KARIBIN NUXHIB DA’WETEKE WE NETTEBI’I ER-RUSULE ‘EWELEM TEKUNU ‘EKSEMTUM MIN KABLU MA LEKUM MIN ZEWALIN
  14,45,WE SEKENTUM FI MESAKINIL-LEDHINE DHELEMU ‘ENFUSEHUM WE TEBEJJENE LEKUM KEJFE FE’ALNA BIHIM WE DEREBNA LEKUMUL-’EMTHALE
  14,46,WE KAD MEKERU MEKREHUM WE ‘INDEL-LAHI MEKRUHUM WE ‘IN KANE MEKRUHUM LITEZULE MINHUL-XHIBALU
  14,47,FELA TEHSEBENNEL-LAHE MUHLIFE WA’DIHI RUSULEHU ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘AZIZUN DHU ENTIKAMIN
  14,48,JEWME TUBEDDELUL-’ERDU GAJREL-’ERDI WE ES-SEMAWATU WE BEREZU LILLAHIL-WAHIDIL-KAHHARI
  14,49,WE TERAL-MUXHRIMINE JEWME’IDHIN MUKARRENINE FIL-’ESFADI
  14,50,SERABILUHUM MIN KATIRANIN WE TEGSHA WUXHUHEHUMU EN-NARU
  14,51,LIJEXHZIJEL-LAHU KULLE NEFSIN MA KESEBET ‘INNALL-LLAHE SERI’UL-HISABI
  14,52,HADHA BELAGUN LILNNASI WE LIJUNDHERU BIHI WE LIJA’LEMU ‘ENNEMA HUWE ‘ILEHUN WAHIDUN WE LIJEDHDHEKKERE ‘ULUL-’ELBABI